<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Cruz Azul ERP — Infraestructura</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/styles.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/nav', { user: user, active: 'infra', instance: instance }) %>
  <div class="main">
    <div class="topbar">
      <h2>Infraestructura AWS</h2>
      <div class="topbar-right">
        <span class="user-email"><%= user.email %></span>
        <span class="badge badge-info"><%= user.role %></span>
        <a class="logout-link" href="/logout">Cerrar sesión</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Instancia actual</h3>
          <div class="stat-value" style="font-size:16px"><%= instance %></div>
          <div class="stat-label">EC2 atendiéndote ahora</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Balanceador</h3>
          <div class="stat-value" style="font-size:14px"><%= albDns %></div>
          <div class="stat-label">Application Load Balancer · :80 → :3000</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Auto Scaling Group</h3>
          <div class="stat-value"><%= asgDesired %></div>
          <div class="stat-label">Deseadas <%= asgDesired %> · Mín <%= asgMin %> · Máx <%= asgMax %></div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Escalado</h3>
          <div class="stat-value"><%= scalingPolicy %></div>
          <div class="stat-label">Target Tracking CPU</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card" style="margin-top:16px">
        <h3>Arquitectura por capas</h3>
        <pre>
  Internet
      │
  ┌───▼──────────┐
  │  ALB (:80)   │  Aplication Load Balancer
  └───┬──────────┘
      │
  ┌───▼──────────┐
  │  Web ERP     │  Auto Scaling Group (min 1 / desired 4 / max 8)
  │  EC2 × 4     │  Subredes privadas · SG-Web
  └───┬──────────┘
      │
  ┌───▼──────────┐
  │  PostgreSQL  │  IaaS dockerizado · EC2 t3.micro
  │  IP: <%= dbHost %>  │  Subred privada · SG-DB
  └──────────────┘

  Monitoreo: Amazon CloudWatch · Alarmas CPU ≥60% y ≤20%
  Seguridad: AAA (JWT) + MFA (TOTP) + Security Groups + subredes privadas</pre>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>